Package: superintronic
Type: Package
Title: Tools for Working with Intron Signal
Version: 0.99.1
Authors@R: c(
    person("Stuart", "Lee", email = "lee.s@wehi.edu.au", role = c("aut", "cre")),
    person("Charity", "Law", email = "law@wehi.edu.au", role = c("aut"))
    )
Maintainer: Stuart Lee <lee.s@wehi.edu.au>
Description: 
    superintronic stimates coverage over intronic/exonic regions within
    genes given an annotation and an experimental design. It allows the 
    user to quickly summarise any intron signal, and visualise the
    coverage regions with their gene context. 
Imports: 
